180
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,780
So what if you have pre-sales?

181
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:23,320
You'll still lose to me in the end.

182
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:31,360
Mother.

183
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:34,160
This is the 80,000 taels

184
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:36,130
I managed to gather within a month.

185
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:39,160
Together with the 5,000 taels from the other shops,

186
00:09:39,160 --> 00:09:41,890
it’s just enough to cover the mansion's deficit.

187
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,040
Xizhao.

188
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:47,200
Thank you for your hard work these days.

189
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:48,520
Mother.

190
00:09:49,040 --> 00:09:50,440
I'm glad you're satisfied.

191
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:52,760
I didn't let you down.

192
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,120
I'm satisfied.

193
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,880
I'm satisfied.

194
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:57,920
This child

195
00:09:57,920 --> 00:09:59,400
is indeed wise.

196
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,870
It's been a long time since I've seen Mother this happy.

197
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:03,560
With Xizhao managing the household,

198
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:05,620
Mother can finally enjoy some peace.

